hadiths[34]{hadithnumber,text}:
2089,"imam Malik-bin-Anas aur Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid Urwa se hadis sunai unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaane mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhney ke liye qiyam farmaya aur bahut hi lamba qiyam kiya, phir aap ne rukoo kiya to intihai lamba rukoo kiya phir aap ne sar uthaya to intihai lamba qiyam kiya aur wo pahley qiyam se ( kuchh ( kam tha phir aap ne ( dobara ( rukoo kiya to bahut lamba rukoo kiya aur wo pahley rukoo se kam tha phir aap ne sajdey kiye phir aap khadey ho gaey aur qiyam ko lamba kiya wo pahley qiyam se kam tha phir aap ne rukoo kiya aur rukoo ko lamba kiya aur wo pahley rukoo se kam tha. phir aap ne apna sar uthaya aur qiyam kiya to bahut lamba qiyam kiya. jabke wo pahley qiyam se kam tha phir aap ne rukoo kiya to intihai lamba rukoo kiya lekin wo pahley rukoo se kam tha. phir sajdey kiye phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (namaz se farigh ho kar) paltey to suraj roshan ho chuka tha. aur aap ne logon se Khitab farmaya Allah Taala ki hamdo-sana bayan ki, phir farmaya : be-shak suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein se hain unko kisi ki maut ya zindagi ki wjah se girahan nahi lagta. jab tum unhein (is haalat mein) dekho to Allah ki badaai bayan karo. Allah Taala se dua maango, Namaz padho aur sadqa karo. aey ummat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) koi nahi jo (is baat par) Allah Taala se zyada ghairat rakhney wala ho ke uska banda ya uski baandi zina karey ! aey ummat Muhammad ! Allah ki qism ! agar tum un baton ko jaan lo jinko main janta hun. to tum bahut zyada ro'o aur bahut kam hanso. dekho ! kya maine ( paigham ( achhi tarah pahuncha diya ? aur Imam Malik ki riwayat mein hai : yaqinan suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain."
2090,abu-Muawiya ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis ki tarah ( riwayat ki aur is mein ye izafa kiya phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ammaa ba'd! ( hamd w Salat (Durud) ke baad) ! bila shubah suraj aur chaand Allah ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain. aur ye bhi izafa kiya : phir aap ne apne donon haath uthaey aur farmaya : aey Allah ! kya maine ( paigham ( achi tarah pahuncha diya ?
2091,"Hurmala-bin-Yahya ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, (kaha ( mujhey ibne- Wahab ne Yunus se khabar di neez abu-Taahir aur Muhammad-bin Salma Muradi ne kaha : ibne- Wahab ne Yunus se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hayaat mubaraka mein suraj ko girahan laga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar masjid mein tashrif le gaey. aap Namaz ke liye khadey ho gaey aur takbeer kahi aur log aap ke peechhey saf basta ho gaey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne lambi qirat farmai, phir aap ne ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha aur aik lamba rukoo kiya phir aap ne apna sar uthaya aur) سمع الله لمن حمده ربنا ولك الحمد ( kaha, phir aap ne qiyam kiya aur aik lambi qirat ki. ye pehli ( qirat ( se kuchh kam thi, phir (Allahu-akbar) keh kar lamba rukoo kiya ye pahley rukoo se kuchh kam tha phir ( سمع الله لمن حمده ربنا ولك الحمد ( kaha. phir sajda kiya aur abu-Taahir ne ( phir aap ne sajda kiya (ke alfaz nahi kahey . phir dusri rakaat mein bhi isi tarah kiya yahan tak ke char rukoo aur char sajdey mukammal kiye aur aap ke salam pherney se pahley suraj roshan ho gaya. phir aap khadey huey aur logon ko khitab farmaya aur Allah Taala ki) aisi ( sana bayan ki jo iske shaayaane shaan thi. phir farmaya suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain. unhein kisi ki maut ki wjah se girahan lagta hai na kisi ki zindagi ki wjah se jab tum unhein ( girahan mein) dekho to fauran Namaz ki taraf lapko . aap ne ye bhi farmaya : aur Namaz padhtey raho yahan tak ke Allah tumharey liye kushadgi kar de aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine apni is jagah ( par hotey huey) har wo cheez dekh li jiska tumharey sath wada kiya gaya hai. yahan tak ke maine apne aapko dekha ke main jannat ka aik guchchaa lena chahta hun us waqt jab tum ne mujhey dekha tha ke main qadam aagey badha raha hun aur) Muhammad-bin Salma ( Muradi ne aagey badh raha hun kaha.  aur maine jahannam bhi dekhi uska aik hissey doosrey hissey ko reza-reza kar raha tha ye us waqt jab tum ne mujhey dekha ke main peechhey hata aur maine jahannam mein Amr-bin-luhyii ko dekha. jisne sabse pahley buton ki nazar ki oontniyan chhodein. abu-Taahir ki riwayat Namaz ki taraf lapko par khatm ho gaee unhon-ne baad wala hissey bayan nahi kiya."
2092,"abu-Amr-Auzai aur unke ilawa doosrey ( rawi , donon mein se har aik ( ne kaha : maine ibne-Shahab Zohri se suna, wo Urwa se aur wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar de rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein suraj ko grahan lag gaya to aap ne ye elaan karne wala (eik shakhs) bheja ke Namaz jama karne wali hai. is par log jama ho gaey, aap aagey badhey , takbeer tahreema kahi aur char ruku'on aur char sajdon ke sath do rakatein padhein."
2093,"Abdur-Rehman-bin namir ne khabar di ke unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se suna, wo Urwa aur Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar de rahe they ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Salat (Durud) ( chaand ya suraj girahan ki Namaz ( mein buland awaz se qirat ki aur do rakaton mein char rukoo aur char sajdey karke Namaz ada ki."
2094,( Abdur-Rehman-bin namir ne hi kaha : ( Zohri ne kaha : kaseer-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne (apne bhai Hazrat Abdullah) Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne do rakaton mein char rukoo aur char sajdey kiye.
2095,"Muhammad-bin-Waleed Zubaidi ne Zohri se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : kaseer-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) hadis bayan kartey they ke Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) rasool akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki suraj girahan waley din ki Namaz (usi tarah) bayan kartey they jis tarah Urwa ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan ki."
2096,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : maine ata (-bin-abi-ribaah ( ko kehtey huey suna : maine Ubaid-bin-Umair se suna, keh rahe they : mujh se us shakhsiyat ne hadis bayan ki jinhein main sachcha samajhta hun. ( Ata ne kaha : ( mera khayal hai unki murad Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se thi. ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya to aap ne bada pur mashaqqat qiyam kiya. seedhey khadey hotey , phir rukoo mein chaley jatey, phir khadey hotey, phir rukoo kartey, phir khadey hotey, phir rukoo kartey. do rakatein  teen rukoo aur char sajdon ke sath padhein. phir aap ne salam phera  to suraj roshan ho chuka tha. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rukoo kartey to ( Allahu-akbar ( kehtey iske baad jab rukoo kartey aur jab sar uthatey to ( سمع الله لمن حمده ( kehtey. uskey baad aap ( khutbe ke liye) khadey huey. Allah Taala ki hamd w sana bayan ki, phir farmaya : suraj aur chaand na kisi ki maut par be noor hotey hain aur na hi kisi ki zindagi par balke wo Allah ki nishaniyan hain. unke zariey se wo apne bandon ko khof dilata hai, jab tum girahan dekho to Allah ko yad karo yahan tak ke wo roshan ho jaaein."
2097,"Qatada ne Ata-bin-abi-Ribah se, unhon-ne Ubaid-bin-Umair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne( chand grahan aur suraj grahan ( kusoof mein)) chh (6) ruku'on aur char sajdon par mushtamil Namaz padhi."
2098,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne Yahya (bin-Saeed ( se aur unhon-ne Umra se riwayat ki ke aik Yahudi aurat Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas maangney ke liye aai. us ne ( aa kar) kaha : Allah aapko azaabe-qabr se panah de. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! logon ko qabar mein azab hoga ? Umra ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main Allah ki panah chahta hun phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik subah kisi sawari par Sawar ho kar nikley to suraj ko grahan lag gaya. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : main bhi aurton ke saath hujron ke darmyan se nikal kar masjid mein aai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari se ( utar kar) Namaz padhney ki us jagah par aaey jahan aap Namaz padhaayaa kartey they. aap khadey ho gaey aur log bhi aap ke peechhey khadey ho gaey. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : phir aap ne lamba qiyam kiya, phir rukoo kiya aur lamba rukoo kiya, phir ( rukoo se) sar uthaya aur lamba qiyam kiya jo pahley qiyam se chhota tha aur phir ( rukoo se) sar uthaya to suraj roshan ho chuka tha. phir (namaz se faraghat ke baad) aap ne farmaya : maine tumhen dekha hai ke tum qabron mein dajjal ki aazmaish ki tarah aazmaish mein daley jaogey . Umra ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke main iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna karti thi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aag ke azab se aur qabr ke azab se panah maangtey they."
2099,abdul-wahaab aur Sufiyan ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se isi sanad ke sath Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki.
2100,"Ismail-ibne-Ulaih ne Hisham dustwaai se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein aik intihai garm din suraj ko grahan lag gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sathiyon ( sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) (ke sath Namaz padhi, aap ne ( itna ( lamba qiyam kiya ke kuchh log girney lagey. phir aap ne rukoo kiya aur usey lamba kiya, phir ( rukoo se) sar uthaya aur lamba ( qiyam ( kiya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir rukoo kiya aur lamba kya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( rukoo se) sar uthaya aur (is qiyam ko lamba ( kiya. phir do sajdey kiye, phir aap (doosri rakaat ke liye) uthey aur isi tarah kiya, is tarah char rukoo aur char sajdey ho gaey. phir aap ne farmaya : bila shubah mujh par har wo cheez ( hashr-nashr , pul siraat , jannat aur dozakh ( jis mein se tum guzrogey , pesh ki gaee. mere samney jannat pesh ki gaee yahan tak ke agar main usmein se aik guchchhey ko lena chahta to usey pakad leta . ya aap ne ( yun ( farmaya : maine aik guchchha lena chaha to mera hath us tak na pahuncha. aur mere samney jahannam pesh ki gaee to maine usmein Bani-Israeel ki aik aurat dekhi jisey apni billi (ke mamley ( mein azab diya ja raha tha. us ne usey baandh diya na usey kuchh khilaaya ( pilaya ( na usey chhoda hi ke wo zamin ke chhotey-motey jaandaar parindey wghaira kha leti aur maine abu Samama Amr (bin-Aamir ( bin-Malik (jiska laqab luhayii tha aur khuza'aa uski aulad mein se tha) ko dekha ke wo aag main apni antadiyaan ghaseet raha tha, log kaha kartey they ke suraj aur chaand kisi azeem shakhsiyat ki maut par hi be noor hotey hain. halanke wo Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain. jo wo tumhen dikhaataa hai, jab unhein girahan lagey to us waqt tak Namaz padhtey raho ke wo (girahan) chhat jaey."
2101,"abdul-Malik-bin-Sabaah ne Hisham dustwaai se isi sanad ke sath usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : (aap ne farmaya : ( maine aag mein balaad hameer ki) rehney wali) aik siyah lambi aurat dekhi aur unhon-ne  (Bani-Israeel ki) ke alfaz nahi kahey ."
2102,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : ham se Abdullah-bin-Numair ne hadis bayan ki, isi ke saath Muhammad-bin-Abdullah Numer ne hadis bayan ki. donon ke lafz miltey-jultey hain. kaha : hamein mere walid ( Abdullah-bin-Numair ( ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Abdul-Malik ne Ata se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein, jis din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke betey Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey, suraj girahan ho gaya. ( kuchh ( logon ne kaha : suraj ko girahan Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ki maut ki bina par laga hai. ( phir ( Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur logon ko chh (6) ruku'on , char sajdon ke sath ( 2 rakaat ( Namaz padhai. shuruat ki to ( Allahu-akbar ( kaha, phir qirat ki aur lambi qirat ki, phir jitna qiyam kiya tha taqriban itna rukoo kiya. phir rukoo se  apna sar uthaya aur pehli qirat se kuchh kam qirat ki, phir (is ( qiyam jitna rukoo kya. phir rukoo se apna sar uthaya aur dusri qirat se kuchh kam qirat ki. phir (is ( qiyam jitna rukoo kya, phir rukoo se apna sar uthaya. phir sajdey ke liye jhukey aur do sajdey farmaai , phir khadey huey aur (is dusri rakaat mein bhi) teen rukoo kiye. unmein se har pahlaa rukoo baad waley rukoo se zyada lamba tha aur aap ka rukoo taqriban sajdey ke barabar tha. phir aap peechhey hatey to aap ke peechhey wali safain bhi peechhey hat gain yahan tak ke ham log aakhir ( aakhiri kinarey ( tak pahunch gaey Abu-Bakar ( ibne-Abi-Sheba ( ne kaha : yahan tak ke aap aurtoon ki safon ke qarib pahunch gaey. phir aap aagey badhey aur aap ke sath log bhi) safon mein) aagey badh aaey yahan tak ke aap ( wapas ( apni jagah par khadey ho gaey phir jab aap ne Namaz se salam phera , us waqt suraj apni aslii haalat par aa chuka tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya : logo ! suraj aur chaand Allah ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hi hain aur bila shubah un donon ko , logon mein se kisi ki maut par girahan nahi lagta Abu-Bakar (bin abi Sheba ( ne kisi insan ki maut par kaha. to jab tum koi aisi cheez dekho to us waqt tak Namaz padho jab tak ke ye zaayel ho jaey. koi cheez nahi jiska tum se wada kiya gaya hai magar maine usey apni is Namaz mein dekh liya hai. aag ( mere samney ( laai gaee aur ye us waqt hua jab tum ne mujhey dekha ke main us dar se peechhey hata hon ke uski lapteyn mujh tak na pahunchein . yahan tak ke maine us aag mein mudey huey sirey wali chhadi ke Malik ko dekh liya, wo aag main apni antadiyaan kheench raha hai. wo apni us mudey huey sirey wali chhadi ke zariey se haajiyon ki) cheezein ( chori karta tha. agar us (ki chori (ka pata chal jata to keh deta : ye cheez meri laathii ke sath atak gaee thi, aur agar pata na chalta to wo usey ley jata. yahan tak ke maine us ( aag ( mein billi wali us aurat ko bhi dekha jisne us ( billi ( ko baandhey rakha , na khud usey kuchh khilaaya aur na usey chhoda ke wo zamin ke chhotey-motey jaandaar aur parindey kha leti. yahan tak ke wo ( billi ( bhook se mar gaee. phir jannat ko) mere samney ( laya gaya aur ye us waqt hua jab tum ne mujhey dekha ke main aagey badha yahan tak ke main wapas apni jagah par aa khada hua. maine apna hath badhaya aur main chahta tha ke main uske phal mein se kuchh ley-loon taake tum usey dekh sako. phir mujh par baat khuli ke main aisa na karun koi aisi cheez nahi jiska tum se wada kiya jata hai magar maine wo apni us Namaz mein dekh li hai."
2103,"hamein ( Abdullah ( ibne-Numair ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham se Hisham ne, unhon-ne (apni biwi ( Fatima ( binte-munzir-bin-Zubair-bin-Awaam ( se aur unhon-ne (apni daadi (Hazrat Asma binte abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein suraj ko grahan lag gaya. chunanche main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan aai aur wo ( sath masjid mein) Namaz padh rahi thin, maine puchha : logon ko kya hua wo (is waqt) Namaz padh rahe hain? unhon-ne apne sar se aasman ki taraf ishara kya. to maine puchha : koi nishani (zahir hui) hai? unhon-ne ( ishaarey se) bataya : haan , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qiyam ko bahut zyada lamba kiya yahan tak ke mujh par ghashii taarii honey lagi. maine apne pahlu mein padi mashk uthai aur apne sar yaa apne chehrey par pani dalney lagi kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz se farigh huey to suraj roshan ho chuka tha. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se Khitab farmaya, Allah Taala ki hamd ki aur uski sana bayan ki, phir farmaya : am'ma-baad ( hamd w sana ke baad) ! koi cheez aisi nahi jiska maine mushaahida nahi kiya tha magar ab maine apni is jagah se iska mushaahida kar liya hai. yahan tak ke jannat aur dozakh bhi dekh li hain. aur ye bhi haqiqat hai ke mujh par ye wahi ki gaee hai ke an-qareeb qabron mein tumhari aazmaish dajjal ki aazmaish ke qareeb ya us jaisi aazmaish hogi.  ( Fatima ne kaha ( mujhey pata nahi, Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne unmein se kon sa lafz kaha, aur tum mein se har aik ke paas ( farishton ki) aamad hogi aur puchha jaeyga : tum us aadmi ke barey mein kya jantey ho? to momin ya yaqin rakhney wala. mujhey malum nahi Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne kon sa lafz kaha.  kahega : wo Muhammad hain, wo Allah ke rasool hain, hamarey paas khuli nishaniyan aur hidayat lekar aaey, ham ne un (ki baat ( ko qabool kya aur itaat ki, teen baar ( sawal w jawab ( hoga. phir us se kaha jaeyga : so jao, hamein malum tha ke tum un par eman rakhtey ho. aik nek bakht ki tarah so jao. aur raha munafiq ya wo jo shak w shuba mein mubtala tha. malum nahi Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) ne unmein se kon sa lafz kaha, to wo kahega : main nahi janta, maine logon ko kuchh kehtey huey suna tha to wahi keh diya tha."
2104,"abu-Usama ne Hisham se, unhon-ne Fatima se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aai to us waqt log (namaz mein) khadey they aur wo bhi Namaz padh rahi thin. maine puchha : logon ko kya hua? aur) aagey ( Hisham se ibne-Numair ki (pichhli ( hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
2105,"Urwa se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : suraj ke liye ( kasaf ( na kaho , balke ( khasaf (ka lafz istemal karo. ( urdu mein donon ka mana girahan hi hai.)"
2106,"Khalid-bin Haris ne kaha : ham se ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki, ( unhon-ne kaha : ( mujh se Mansoor-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne apni walida Safiya-binte-Sheba se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Asma-binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik din Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tezi se ( lapak kar) gaey. kaha : unki murad us din se thi jis din suraj ko girahan laga tha. to ( jaldi mein) aap ne aik zanaana qameez uthaalii yahan tak ke peechhey se aapko aap ki chadar la kar di gaee. aap ne logon ki imamat kartey huey intihai lamba qiyam kiya. agar koi aisa insan aata jis ko ye pata na hota ke aap ( qiyam ke baad) rukoo kar chukey hain to us qiyam ki lambai ki bina par wo kabhi na keh sakta ke aap (eik baar ( rukoo kar chukey hain."
2107,"Yahya umwii ne kaha : ham se ibine Juraij ne isi sanad ke sath usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki. (is mein) unhon-ne kaha : (aap ne) lamba qiyam kiya, aap qiyam kartey, phir rukoo mein chaley jatey aur is mein ye izafa kiya : main ( baithney ka irada karti to ( aisi aurat ko dekhney lagti jo mujh se badh kar umr raseeda hoti aur kisi dusri ko dekhti jo mujh se zyada bimar hoti. (aur unse hosla pa kar khadi rehti .)"
2108,"Wuhaib ne kaha : hamein Mansoor ne apni walida ( Safiya ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Asma-binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein suraj ko grahan lag gaya to aap jaldi se lapkey (aur ( ghalati se zanaana qamees utha li yahan tak ke uskey baad) peechhey se) aap ki chadar aapko laakar di gaee. kaha : main apni zarurat se farigh hui aur) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar se) masjid mein dakhil hui to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko qiyam ki haalat mein dekha. mein bhi aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein khadi ho gaee. aap ne bahut lamba qiyam kiya yahan tak ke maine apne aapko us haalat mein dekha ke main baithna chahti thi, phir main kisi kamzor aurat ki taraf mutwajjeh hoti aur (dil mein) kehti : ye to mujh se bhi zyada kamzor hai. (aur khadi rehti hai) phir aap ne rukoo kiya to rukoo ko intihai lamba kar diya. phir aap ne ( rukoo se) apna sar uthaya to qiyam ko bahut tool diya. yahan tak ke agar koi aadmi (is haalat mein) aata to usey khayal hota ke abhi tak aap ne rukoo nahi kiya."
2109,"Hafs-bin-Maisra ne kaha : Zaid-bin-Aslam ne mujhey Ata-bin-Yasar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aur aap ke sath logon ne Namaz padhi. aap ne bahut lamba qiyam kiya, sura Baqra ke baqadr , phir aap ne bahut lamba rukoo kiya. phir aap ne sar uthaya aur lamba qiyam kiya aur wo pahley qiyam se kam tha, phir aap ne lamba rukoo kiya aur wo pahley rukoo se kam tha. phir aap ne sajdey kiye. phir aap ne lamba qiyam kiya aur wo pahley qiyam se kuchh kam tha, phir aap ne lamba rukooa kiya aur wo pahley rukoo se kam tha. phir aap ne sar uthaya aur lamba qiyam kiya aur wo apne se pahley waley qiyam se kam tha, phir aap ne lamba rukoo kiya aur wo pahley ke rukoo se kam tha. phir aap ne sajdey kiye, phir aap ne salam phera to suraj roshan ho chuka tha. phir aap ne irshad farmaya : suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki do nishaniyon mein se nishaniyan hain. wo kisi ki maut par girahan zada nahi hotey aur na kisi ki zindagi ke sabab se (unhein girahan lagta hai). jab tum ( unko ( is tarah dekho to Allah ka zikr karo. (namaz padho .) logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap ne apne khadey honey ki us jagah par koi cheez leney ki koshish ki, phir ham ne dekha ke aap ruk gaey. aap ne farmaya : maine jannat dekhi aur maine usmein se aik guchchha lena chaha aur agar main usko pakad leta to tum rehatii duniya tak usmein se khaatey rahtey (aur ( maine jahannam dekhi , maine aaj jaisa manzar kabhi nahi dekha aur maine ahale-jahannam ki aksariyat aurton ki dekhi . logon ne puchha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! (ye ( kis wjah se ? aap ne farmaya : unke kufr ki wjah se. kaha gaya : kya wo Allah ke sath kufr karti hain? aap ne farmaya : rafeeq zindagi ka kufraan ( na-shukri ( karti hain. aur ehsan ka kufraan kar tii hain. agar tum unmein se kisi ke sath hamesha husne-suluk kartey raho phir wo tum se kisi din koi ( na-gawar ( baat dekhey to keh degi : tum se maine kabhi koi khair nahi dekhi ."
2110,"Imam Malik ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se isi sanad ke sath us (mazkura (uper zikr) hadis) ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta unhon-ne   ((ثم رايناك كففت (ke bajaey) ( ثم رايناك تكعكعت ( ) phir ham ne aapko dekha ke aap aagey badhney se baaz rahe ( kaha hai."
2111,"Ismail-ibne-Ulaih ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Habib-bin-abi Sabit se, unhon-ne Taaus se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab suraj ko girahan laga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne char sajdon ke sath aath (8) rukoo kiye aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi usi ki tarah riwayat ki gaee hai."
2112,"Yahya ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Habib ne Taaus se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne kusoof (ke doran ( mein Namaz padhai , qirat ki phir rukoo kiya, phir qirat ki, phir rukoo kiya, phir qirat ki, phir rukoo kiya, phir qirat ki, phir rukoo kiya, phir sajdey kiye. kaha : dusri ( rakaat ( bhi isi tarah thi."
2113,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein girahan hua to ( الصلواة جامعة ( (jama karne wali Namaz ke alfaz ke saath) elaan kiya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik rakaat mein do rukoo kiye, phir dusri rakaat ke liye khadey ho gaey aur aik rakaat mein do rukoo kiye, phir suraj se girahan zaayel kar diya gaya to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine na kabhi aisa rukoo kiya aur na kabhi aisa sajda kiya jo us se zyada lamba ho."
2114,"Hushaim ne Ismail se, unhon-ne Qais-bin-abi-Hazim se, aur unhon-ne abu Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain. Allah Taala unke zariey se apne bandon ko khof dilata hai. aur un donon ko insanon mein se kisi ki maut ki bina par girahan nahi lagta. lihaza jab tum unmein se koi nishani dekho to Namaz padho aur Allah Taala ko pukaaro yahan tak ke jo kuchh tumharey ( sath hua) hai wo khul jaey."
2115,"Moatamir ne Ismail se, unhon-ne Qais se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : suraj aur chaand ko logon mein se kisi ke marney par girahan nahi lagta balke wo Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain. lihaza jab tum us ( girahan ( ko dekho to qiyam karo aur Namaz padho."
2116,"Wakee , abu-Usama , ibne-Numair , Jareer, Sufiyan , aur Marwan sab ne Ismail se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, Sufiyan aur Wakee ki riwayat mein hai ke Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ke din suraj ko girahan laga to logon ne kaha : suraj ko Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ki bina par girahan laga hai."
2117,"abu-Aamir Ash-ari Abdullah-bin baraad aur Muhammad-bin Alaa ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne bareed se hadis sunai, unhon-ne abu-Burda se aur unhon-ne abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein suraj ko girahan lag gaya to aap tezi se uthey , aapko khof laahiq hua ke mubaada qiyamat ( aa gai) ho, yahan tak ke aap masjid mein tashrif ley aaey aur aap khadey huey bahut lamba qiyam , rukoo aur sajdey ke sath Namaz padhtey rahe, maine kabhi aapko nahi dekha tha ke kisi Namaz mein (aap ne) aisa kiya ho, phir aap ne farmaya : yahi nishaniyan hain jo Allah Taala bhejta hai. ye kisi ki maut ya zindagi ki bina par nahi hotin. balke Allah inko bhejta hai taake inke zariey se apne bandon ko (qiyamat se) khof dilaaey. isliye jab tum inmein se koi nishani dekho to jald az jald iske zikr , dua aur istighfar ki taraf lapko , ibne- Alaa ki riwayat main (خسفت الشمس) ke bajaey (كسفت الشمس ( ) suraj ko girahan laga (ke alfaz hain ( mana aik hi hai) aur unhon-ne ( يخوف بها Ubada ( unke zariey se apne bandon ko khof dilata hai ke bajaey) ( يخوف Ubada ( (apne bandon ko khof dilata hai) kaha,"
2118,"Bishr-bin-Mufazzal ne kaha : jureri ne hamein abul-Ala-hayyaan-bin-Umair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi main apne teeron ke zariey se teer andazi kar raha tha ke suraj ko girahan lag gaya, to maine unko phainkaa aur (dil mein) kaha ke main aaj har sura dekhunga ke suraj girahan mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par kya nai kaifiyat taarii hoti hai? main aap ke paas pahuncha to ( dekha ke) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hath uthaey huey they, ( Allah ko) pukar rahe they, uski badaai bayan kar rahe they, uski hamd w sana bayan kar rahe they aur Laa-ilah-illal-Alaah (لاالٰہ الا اللہ کا) ka wird farma rahe they, yahan tak ke suraj se girahan hata diya gaya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (har rakaat mein) do soortein padhein aur do rakatein ada kin."
2119,"Abdul-Aala-bin-Abdul-Aala ne jureri se, unhon-ne hayyaan-bin-Umair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) mein se they, unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein aik din Madina main apne teeron se nishaaney laga raha tha ke achcha suraj ko girahan lag gaya, is par maine unhein ( teeron ko) phainkaa aur (dil mein) kaha : Allah ki qism ! main zaroor dekhoon ga ke suraj ke girahan ke is waqt mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par kya nai kaifiyat taarii hui hai? kaha : main aap ke paas aaya, aap Namaz mein khadey they, donon hath uthaey huey they, phir aap ne tasbeeh , hamd w sana ''لا الہ الا اللہ'' aur Allah ki badaai ka wird aur dua maangnii shuru kar di yahan tak ke suraj ka girahan chhat gaya, kaha : aur jab suraj ka girahan chhat gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne do soortein padhein aur do rakaat Namaz ada ki."
2120,"Saalim-bin Nuh ne kaha : hamein jureri ne hayyaan-bin-Umair se khabar di aur unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik baar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein bahar nikal kar apne teeron se nishana bazi ki mashq kar raha tha ke suraj girahan ho gaya, phir ( Saalim-bin Nuh ne) un donon ( Bishr aur Abdul-Aala ( ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
2121,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye khabar sunaya kartey they. ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yaqinan suraj aur chaand ko kisi shakhs ki maut ya zindagi ki wjah se girahan nahi lagta balke ye Allah ki nishaniyon mein se nishani hain, jab tum unhein (is tarah) dekho to Namaz padho ."
2122,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein suraj ko girahan laga, isi din jab Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : suraj aur chaand Allah Taala ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain, unko na kisi ki maut se girahan lagta hai aur na kisi ki zindagi se isliye jab tum unko ( girahan laga ( dekho to Allah ko pukaaro aur Namaz padho yahan tak ke girahan zaayel ho jaey."
